# Citation information for IRIM R Workshops: Introduction to R

## Citing This Workshop

If you use or adapt this workshop material, please cite it as:

  Kathryn Napier (2026). IRIM R Workshops: Introduction to R.
  Independent Research Institute of Mongolia (IRIM).
  https://github.com/IRIM-Mongolia/irim-r-workshops


